## Voice Selection Guidelines

### Voice Characteristics

**For Casual Tone**:
- Warm, friendly voice
- Conversational pace
- Natural, relaxed delivery
- Approachable personality

**For Professional Tone**:
- Clear, authoritative voice
- Professional pace
- Confident, credible delivery
- Trustworthy personality

### Voice Settings

**Recommended Settings**:
- **Stability**: 0.6-0.7 (balanced between natural and consistent)
- **Similarity**: 0.75-0.85 (maintains voice characteristics)
- **Style**: 0.3-0.5 (moderate expressiveness)

**For Casual Tone**:
- Higher style (0.5-0.7) for more expressiveness
- Slightly lower stability (0.5-0.6) for natural variation

**For Professional Tone**:
- Lower style (0.2-0.4) for more controlled delivery
- Higher stability (0.7-0.8) for consistency

